=== Planyo online reservations - WooCommerce integration ===
Plugin Author: Xtreeme GmbH
Contributors: xtreeme
Donate link: No Thanks
Tags: woocommerce,shopping,cart,reservation, booking, system, reserve, book, software,scheduling, schedule,online,event,accommodation,appointment
